        <abstract> 
<p>Duchenne [<hi rend="italic">Mécanisme</hi>] has arrived. Has been testing the photographs with 20 or 30 persons; when all or nearly all agree with Duchenne, CD trusts him. Not one understood the "contracted pyramidal of the nose". CD does not think the so-called muscle of lasciviousness worth exhibiting.</p>  
<p>His MS [of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] is so large he may print only what he has, and make a second volume of what he is now writing on expression.</p> 
            <p>Discusses photographs he would like to have: baby screaming, person in paroxysm of fear.</p>
        </abstract>
